title: BRIEF-230 games, apps in Examobile's portfolio at end of Sept.
text:
BRIEF-230 games, apps in Examobile's portfolio at end of Sept. 
Oct 6 Examobile SA : 
* In 3 quarters of 2015 total number of advertisements display in company's applications exceeded 218.9 million 
* At end of Sept. 2015 company had over 230 games and applications in its portfolio 
* Total number of unique installations of company's applications on mobile devices at end of Sept. 2015 at over 20.9 million Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
